      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the 996.2 generation's mechanical zenith. Power is delivered by a naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus valve timing, paired with a tactile G96 six-speed manual gearbox. This specimen has been fastidiously curated, featuring a proactively addressed IMS bearing and a pristine rear main seal. The chassis dynamics are factory-perfect, utilizing the wide-body\u2019s enhanced track width and Turbo-derived braking system with four-piston monobloc calipers. The AWD system\u2019s viscous coupling provides impeccable torque distribution, ensuring neutral handling under load. Finished in concours-grade paint with an interior devoid of typical wear, this C4S represents a rare opportunity for the collector seeking mechanical perfection and uncompromising performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
